{
  "stem": "16473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I'm sure I was conflicted.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I can't say anything about that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I must have been very conflicted to know how I should feel or what I should feel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was your reaction, being a very young child and having to live this secret life, that this man was your father and yet he wasn't your father?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How did that affect you as when you were in the basement, in the bunker?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know how it affected me in later life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, I hate hypocrisy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I will not stand for hypocrisy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I go out of my way to say what I am and who I am.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I don't know how I felt as a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, that that's an interesting story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was in a work camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "At one point in time, when the people in the work camp were going to be taken to the concentration camp, the Hungarian guards-- these were not the Nyilas.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were just the guards guarding these people-- let people go, provided they paid.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My father had nothing to pay with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father was a very meek man and not a courageous man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The guy in front of him paid, he walked right behind that guy who paid and just walked out.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he knew where to go because, when we visited my mother, we told him where we were, so he followed us there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But of course, getting there, he could not be my father, he could not be my mother's husband.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he was designated as the uncle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And uncle, being my mother's brother, would mean that they could show some affection toward each other and they could, you know, interact with each other.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
